title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Aug 9 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 1: New York Times reporter lets the covid out of the bag: Obama’s Birthday Bash Safe Because It Was A "Sophisticated, Vaccinated Crowd." Fauci silent on indoor Obama party, slams outdoor Sturgis motorcycle rally. Buck goes into detail explaining the American troop withdrawal, and the Taliban take over Afghanistan. Bill Maher takes on the left for silencing the Wuhan lab leak. Callers weigh in on Afghanistan.
